data.title: This place was a godsend for late night dinner!
data.text: All the other restaurants were closed and we tried Banker's Casino.  Well the food was really good and they are open really late.  We had burgers - they were cooked to order and very tasty. This place is great and I highly recommend eating there - we'll be going back, for sure.

data.title: what a dump
data.text: you know what daddy said, if you cant say something nice, then don't say nothing at all. I would prefer they change this building into a animal rescue or something useful to our community, live's are ruined, marriages destroyed, and families crumbled over the activities that take place here.
